<div id="tutorial-editor-overlay-screen" class="container-inner screen-overlay">
	<div id="tutorial-editor-overlay-inner" class="row center">
		<span id="tutorial-editor-overlay-title">Rules</span>
		<span class="tutorial-editor-overlay-note tutorial-editor-overlay-text">
	    Dark purple defense structures will be placed for you on the grid.
	    Your objective is to protect them at all costs.
	    Your enemies are a sickly green color. Select units on the left toolbar and place them on the grid to defend yourself. Enemies will only spawn in the gray area, and you can only place units in the white.
	    Press the play button when you're ready to begin.<br>
	    <button id="tutorial-play" class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large"><i class="wisteria-icons left mdi mdi-play"></i> Play</button>
	    </span>
        <table>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons tplay mdi mdi-play"></i></th>
					<th>Play button - begins the game. Located on the left of the time toolbar.</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons tpause mdi mdi-pause"></i></th>
					<th>Pause button - pauses the game. Located on the left of the time toolbar.</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons tstore mdi mdi-store"></i></th>
					<th>Store button - opens the Ye Olde Shoppe. Displayed after victory/defeat.</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons tback mdi mdi-step-backward"></i></th>
					<th>Back button - choose another level. Displayed after victory/defeat.</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons treplay mdi mdi-replay"></i></th>
					<th>Replay button - replay the level. Displayed on pause/victory/defeat.</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons tshare mdi mdi-share-variant"></i></th>
					<th>Share button - share on social media. Displayed on victory/defeat.</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons thelp mdi mdi-help"></i></th>
					<th>Help button - access this help page. Displayed on pause.</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons tnext mdi mdi-play"></i></th>
					<th>Next button - play the next level. Displayed on victory.</th>
				</tr>
				<tr>
					<th><i class="wisteria-icons tplay mdi mdi-lock"></i></th>
					<th>Cheat code button - enter a cheat code. Located on the right of the time toolbar.</th>
				</tr>

	    </table>
	</div>
</div>

